==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Regorge
<hw>Re*gorge"</hw> <pr>(r?*g?rj")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>regorder</ets>; <ets>re-</ets> + <ets>gorger</ets> to gorge. Cf.
<er>Regurgitate</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To vomit up; to eject from
the stomach; to throw back.</def> <rj><au>Hayward.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To swallow again; to swallow back.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Tides at highest mark <qex>regorge</qex> the flood.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 1211 --></p>

<p><ent>Regrade</ent>⟦br⟧
